{"id":1821,"date":"2023-06-03T12:11:37","date_gmt":"2023-06-03T12:11:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.screeningdate.com\/?p=1821"},"modified":"2024-03-30T17:23:12","modified_gmt":"2024-03-30T17:23:12","slug":"university-of-lethbridge-fees","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/university-of-lethbridge-fees\/","title":{"rendered":"University of Lethbridge Fees 2024"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><em><strong>\u00a0University of Lethbridge Fees 2024 \u2013Fees &amp; Costs. University Fees. Incidental and Ancillary Fees, faculty, Program, Admission Fees<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p><div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_64 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-light-blue ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title \" >Contents on This Page<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/university-of-lethbridge-fees\/#Fees_Category_and_option\" title=\"Fees Category and option\">Fees Category and option<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/university-of-lethbridge-fees\/#How_and_When_to_Pay_Fees\" title=\"How and When to Pay Fees\">How and When to Pay Fees<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/university-of-lethbridge-fees\/#Payment_Method_for_Students_Fees\" title=\"Payment Method for Students Fees\">Payment Method for Students Fees<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/university-of-lethbridge-fees\/#_Registration_time_limit_University_of_Lethbridge_Tuition_Fees\" title=\"\u00a0Registration time limit| University of Lethbridge Tuition Fees\">\u00a0Registration time limit| University of Lethbridge Tuition Fees<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/university-of-lethbridge-fees\/#How_to_Pay_University_of_Lethbridge_Tuition_Fees\" title=\"How to Pay| University of Lethbridge Tuition Fees\">How to Pay| University of Lethbridge Tuition Fees<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/university-of-lethbridge-fees\/#Estimated_Academic_Expense_for_Domestic_Students\" title=\"Estimated Academic Expense for Domestic Students\">Estimated Academic Expense for Domestic Students<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>The University of Lethbridge Payment portal is open for all current and new students applying for admission into the University. The payment directives are given below:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong>Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc81315456\">Fees Category and option<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc81315457\">How and When to Pay Fees<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc81315458\">Registration time limit<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc81315459\">How to Pay<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc81315460\">Estimated Fees and Tuition <\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"fees-category-and-option\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Fees_Category_and_option\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc81315456\"><\/a>Fees Category and option<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>To learn more about fees and student financial services visit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ulethbridge.ca\/future-student\/graduate-studies\/tuition-fees\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-and-when-to-pay-fees\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_and_When_to_Pay_Fees\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc81315457\"><\/a>How and When to Pay Fees<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>How to make payments through online banking <\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Log into your bank\u2019s online system.<\/li>\n<li>Add the University of Lethbridge as a payee on your bill payment profile<\/li>\n<li>Enter your account details<\/li>\n<li>Note that it may take few days for your payment to process.<\/li>\n<li>Your university fees consist of Tuition and others Costs based on your faculty and degree.<\/li>\n<li>To complete registration, you\u2019ll need to pay your fees ahead of\u00a0your Faculty\u2019s registration deadlines.<\/li>\n<li>To pay your University of Lethbridge\u2019s faculty fees click <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ulethbridge.ca\/future-student\/graduate-studies\/tuition-fees\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"payment-method-for-students-fees\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Payment_Method_for_Students_Fees\"><\/span>Payment Method for Students Fees<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Online using UR self-service. Payments can be made with a visa, MasterCard, or American Express credit card using UR self-service.<\/li>\n<li>Through telephone<\/li>\n<li>Mail<\/li>\n<li>In-person<\/li>\n<li>Wire Transfer<\/li>\n<li>Online using Internet Banking<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"registration-time-limit-university-of-lethbridge-tuition-fees\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_Registration_time_limit_University_of_Lethbridge_Tuition_Fees\"><\/span>\u00a0<a name=\"_Toc81315458\"><\/a>Registration time limit| University of Lethbridge Tuition Fees<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>You will need to pay your tuition; incidental and ancillary fees by the date fixed or arrange for a payment deferral if you\u2019ll be receiving the government\u2019s financial aid. Click <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ulethbridge.ca\/future-student\/graduate-studies\/tuition-fees\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a> to view Deadlines.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-pay-university-of-lethbridge-tuition-fees\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Pay_University_of_Lethbridge_Tuition_Fees\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc81315459\"><\/a>How to Pay| University of Lethbridge Tuition Fees<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Find out more supplementary information about Registration Steps and Deadlines, including directions on paying your Fees and Requesting a Tuition Fee Deferral <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ulethbridge.ca\/future-student\/graduate-studies\/tuition-fees\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>For more information about the University of Lethbridge Academic and Other fees visit<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Check <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ulethbridge.ca\/future-student\/graduate-studies\/tuition-fees\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a> for more information about how to enroll, pay fees, and more.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"estimated-academic-expense-for-domestic-students\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Estimated_Academic_Expense_for_Domestic_Students\"><\/span>Estimated Academic Expense for Domestic Students<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"270\">Tuition<\/td>\n<td width=\"372\">$5,690 (2024)<sup>1<\/sup><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"270\">Sport and Recreation Services Fee<\/td>\n<td width=\"372\">$200<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"270\">Students&#8217; Union Fees<\/td>\n<td width=\"372\">$984 (Includes Health and Dental Insurance <sup>2<\/sup> and UPass)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"270\">Meliorist (Student Magazine)<\/td>\n<td width=\"372\">$10<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"270\">Annual total<\/td>\n<td width=\"372\">$7,360<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>For more information visit the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ulethbridge.ca\/future-student\/graduate-studies\/estimated-costs\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Student Financial Assistance<\/a> for guidance, information, tools, and services to help you meet your financial needs or complaints.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00a0See also &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; \u00a0\u00a0<\/strong><a title=\"David Johnston \u2013 Lebovic Foundation International Experience Award\" href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/david-johnston-lebovic-foundation-international-experience-award\/\" rel=\"bookmark nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">David Johnston \u2013 Lebovic Foundation International Experience Award<\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"\u00a0University of Lethbridge Fees 2024 \u2013Fees &amp; Costs. University Fees. Incidental and Ancillary Fees, faculty, Program, Admission Fees&hellip;\n","protected":false